[Gary] Hey, Luke. You working tonight?

00:28:17.196 --> 00:28:18.757
Not tonight. Tonight's a night off.

00:28:18.781 --> 00:28:21.075
- Wait. Is this…
- [grunting]

00:28:21.659 --> 00:28:22.886
- Mm-hmm.
- [grunts]

00:28:22.910 --> 00:28:25.871
Joan? No! [Chuckles]

00:28:26.831 --> 00:28:29.017
- No. [Grunts] No, please.
- Move it!

00:28:29.041 --> 00:28:31.395
[escapee] I can't look at
another goddamn painting.

00:28:31.419 --> 00:28:32.771
- It's so boring.
- [Gary] All right.

00:28:32.795 --> 00:28:34.189
- Well, I better go.
- No! [Grunting]

00:28:34.213 --> 00:28:36.191
- But, hey, you are one lucky lady.
- [Joan] Hmm?

00:28:36.215 --> 00:28:37.275
[security] Gary!

00:28:37.299 --> 00:28:38.443
- Oh.
- Huh.

00:28:38.467 --> 00:28:40.445
- [Gary] Move it. I'm sick of this crap.
- [escapee] No, please!

00:28:40.469 --> 00:28:41.947
[Gary] Get in here now!

00:28:41.971 --> 00:28:43.115
[Luke] Oof.

00:28:43.139 --> 00:28:44.658
Museum World's the worst!

00:28:44.682 --> 00:28:46.142
- [Joan gasps] Oh, God.
- [sighs]

00:28:47.268 --> 00:28:50.539
Oh, my God. [Breathes shakily]
What-What did he do?

00:28:50.563 --> 00:28:52.565
Oh, he tried to escape his eternity.

00:28:53.607 --> 00:28:55.651
Once you've chosen,
you can't go back here.

00:28:56.152 --> 00:28:57.361
You have to get it right.

00:28:58.195 --> 00:29:00.757
- Oh, that's a lot of pressure.
- [sighs] Yeah, it is.

