00:29:56.504 --> 00:29:57.856
I need to think.

00:29:57.880 --> 00:30:00.049
[breathes shakily] Okay?

00:30:06.096 --> 00:30:07.598
[breathing heavily]

00:30:11.644 --> 00:30:12.645
Oh.

00:30:13.437 --> 00:30:14.438
Okay.

